113
00:08:03,833 --> 00:08:05,833
"Sawako Kouzuki (35)"

114
00:08:05,833 --> 00:08:08,233
Terima kasih banyak.

115
00:08:08,233 --> 00:08:09,833
Siapa dia?

116
00:08:09,833 --> 00:08:12,133
Dia anak tunggal Tuan Kouzuki, Sawako.

117
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:16,033
Mungkin peta ini tidak ada hubungannya dengan pencurian,

118
00:08:16,033 --> 00:08:19,233
