132
00:08:57,833 --> 00:09:01,033
Hei, teman-teman, kita bertemu di taman perpustakaan.

133
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:04,133
Kau mau ke mana?

134
00:09:12,833 --> 00:09:14,333
Apa katamu?

135
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:17,533
Tangan korban sangat bau rokok?

136
00:09:17,533 --> 00:09:19,333
Ya, pak. Tidak salah lagi.

137
00:09:19,333 --> 00:09:21,033
Waktu aku tiba di sana,

138
00:09:21,033 --> 00:09:23,533
