139
00:09:23,533 --> 00:09:27,633
Tapi, anaknya mengatakan bahwa dia tidak merokok.

140
00:09:27,633 --> 00:09:31,733
Lagipula, tidak ada puntung rokok di sekitar tempat kejadian.

141
00:09:31,733 --> 00:09:33,833
Aneh.

142
00:09:33,833 --> 00:09:35,233
Rokok.

143
00:09:36,233 --> 00:09:38,333
Conan terlambat sekali.

144
00:09:38,333 --> 00:09:39,833
Selagi kita di sini,

145
00:09:39,833 --> 00:09:41,533
tangan-tangan penjahat itu mungkin...

146
00:09:41,533 --> 00:09:43,833
Kenapa kita tidak mengerjakan sendiri saja...

147
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:47,133
Tunggu sampai Conan kembali.

148
00:09:47,133 --> 00:09:48,333
Oke.

149
00:09:48,333 --> 00:09:50,433
Panas sekali, ya?

150
00:09:50,433 --> 00:09:52,733
Aku ingin es krim, kau juga?

151
00:09:52,733 --> 00:09:55,333
Ada mesin minuman di perpustakaan.

152
00:09:55,333 --> 00:09:57,333
Ayo kita beli minuman.

153
00:09:57,333 --> 00:09:59,133
Bagaimana denganmu, Ai?

154
00:09:59,133 --> 00:10:00,533
Tidak, terima kasih.

155
00:10:00,533 --> 00:10:03,733
-Es krim... -Apa yang harus kubeli?

156
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:31,530
Apa yang mereka lakukan?

157
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:38,430
Tuan Yagisawa, halo.

158
00:10:38,430 --> 00:10:41,430
Halo, Conan, lama tak jumpa.

159
00:10:42,930 --> 00:10:45,530
Cool! Apa kabarmu?

160
00:10:46,530 --> 00:10:48,230
Kau kenal mereka?

161
00:10:48,230 --> 00:10:50,630
Ya Aku berhasil memecahkan sebuah kasus pembunuhan

162
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:53,530
